WEBVTT

00:00.411 --> 00:01.944
<i>Previously on Camelot...</i>

00:03.586 --> 00:07.121
- Are you really a sorcerer?
- I don't care what you believe.

00:07.188 --> 00:09.057
But I've sworn off those powers
a long time ago.

00:09.125 --> 00:12.070
- Why?
- Because they cost.

00:12.138 --> 00:15.615
It's over.
This was it. The once.

00:15.683 --> 00:19.121
Now we must never talk of it.
I have to get ready for my wedding.

00:19.189 --> 00:21.663
Every woman in this village is
protected. By my men,

00:21.731 --> 00:25.167
by my flag.
Exham is now part of Camelot.

00:25.234 --> 00:27.603
We understand
he is your brother,

00:27.671 --> 00:31.543
but the land moves further
into chaos every day.

00:31.611 --> 00:33.511
Everything
that was once so secure

00:33.579 --> 00:36.948
under my father's reign is
now under threat.

00:43.189 --> 00:47.259
♪

